manufacturerProductDescription.media_text: Multiple Modes for Newly Designed Push Puzzle Game Machine: Mission Mode: 30 large missions in total, each large mission containing 5 small mission. More lights will be on as the missions increases, also the time limit for each small mission will be shortened. Memory Mode: 9 large missions in total, each large mission containing 5 small mission. It is necessary to wait for lights to be on at the start of the game. Scoring Mode: press deratization keys according to the lights which are on within 1 min; If you press all ten key, you can't enter the next round unless you press back key. Clever Multi Player Mode: press deratization keys according to the lights which are on; after each player accomplished one mission, the next player begins delivering on mission. (You can find more SPECIFIC ways to play in the manual.) Caution: To increase the difficulty of the gopher game, you need to press the button to the end to eliminate the lights, if you just press the button, there is a probability that the lights will not go out.It will be rusty to use at first. After getting used to its use, it will improve your speed of eliminating lights.Avoid scratching the buttons of this product with pencils, nails or other sharp objects.SIENBOR will solve any problems during use.
